definition: next in sequence/second/the second (day, time etc)/secondary/vice-/sub-/infra-/inferior quality/substandard/order/sequence/hypo- (chemistry)/classifier for enumerated events: time
lit. twice then three times (idiom); fig. repeatedly/over and over again

sentences.english: He won a few headers and calmed things down.
sentences.chinese: 赢得了几次头球争顶并且使情况稳定下来。
发动机好几次发动不起来。

sentences.english: You can enter more than once, if you want.
sentences.chinese: 你们如果愿意的话，也可以多测几次。

sentences.english: Hangzhou been several times, but not visited Lingyin.
sentences.chinese: 杭州已经好几次，但没有到过灵隐寺。

sentences.english: At the beginning they met with much stupidity and apathy.
sentences.chinese: 开始的几次会议他们遭遇了很多麻木和冷漠。

sentences.english: After a couple of brief growth spurts, home prices have started declining again in earnest.
sentences.chinese: 经过几次短暂的增长，房价又实实在在地开始下滑。

sentences.english: I traveled NYC a couple of times with my friends while I was off.
sentences.chinese: 在闲暇之余，我和朋友们一起去纽约游玩过几次。

sentences.english: Tracy was scared by Artest for the last several plays.
sentences.chinese: 阿泰斯特最后几次的表现，麦迪好像被吓到了。

sentences.english: Run some more tests and see me in the morning.
sentences.chinese: 再多做几次测试，明早来见我。

sentences.english: Little feedstuff in the drinking spoon is drunk out after several times of drinking.
sentences.chinese: 饮水勺中的少许饲料经几次饮水即被喝净。

sentences.english: She must see more of him to understand his ways;
sentences.chinese: 她必须和他多见几次面，才能了解他的癖性。

sentences.english: It was one of the few signs of feistiness from China all afternoon.
sentences.chinese: 这是整个下午中国队为数不多的几次过火表现之一。

sentences.english: And after this had happened several times, people stopped employing him as a copyist.
sentences.chinese: 如是几次，叫他钞书的人也没有了。

sentences.english: They asked us to move back a few times but were very nice and sometimes funny about it.
sentences.chinese: 他们问我们搬回了几次，但很不错，有时甚至可笑的。

sentences.english: I went through several tests, phone interviews, and on-site interviews for my various internships and jobs.
sentences.chinese: 我经历过好几次测试，电话面试和网上面试。

sentences.english: The paper introduced the situation of underground debris flow in Chengchao Mine.
sentences.chinese: 介绍了程潮铁矿几次井下泥石流发生情况。
